    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the robust 3.8L DFI flat-six engine. This example exhibits zero bore scoring and maintains impeccable factory tolerances. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain delivers 385 hp with linear power delivery and a visceral 7,500 RPM redline. Equipped with PASM for adaptive damping and a mechanical limited-slip differential, the chassis remains taut with no bushing fatigue. The exterior retains its original depth and luster, while the undercarriage remains dry, showing no signs of thermal cycling stress or fluid seepage. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning collector.",
